                                    <h3 class="card-title">Development</h3>
                                    <p class="card-desc">Configuring the Odoo platform and developing bespoke modules adapted to your requirements with clean, scalable code.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Phase 4 -->
                            <div class="col-lg-4 phase-block" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                                <div class="kinetic-card">
                                    <div class="card-bg-number">04</div>
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Integration &amp; Testing</h3>
                                    <p class="card-desc">Seamlessly migrating legacy data and integrating systems with rigorous testing to ensure a stable transformation.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Phase 5 -->
                            <div class="col-lg-4 phase-block" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                                <div class="kinetic-card">
                                    <div class="card-bg-number">05</div>
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Launch &amp; Support</h3>
                                    <p class="card-desc">Full system switch-on with dedicated team training and ongoing proactive maintenance to optimize your investment.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
